{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/nubank/nuconta","webpackCompilationHash":"d49941d1904f17ebdb2f","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>NuConta is an unprecedented mix of current, savings, and payments accounts, all-in-one. Thanks to a one-year-long co-creative process, our team was able to design and ship a product that uniquely addresses customer needs.</p>\n<div style=\"background: #BB6BD9\" class=\"w-100 pa4 tc mt5 flex\">\n<img class=\"w-50 flex br2 mw5 center \" src=\"/nuconta-001-d9da2e4891a960f4af48a7abc699714c.gif\">\n</div>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 003\"\n        title=\"nuconta 003\"\n        src=\"/static/b4576ddc1d9bf0630052d48d69d817d2/79a4a/nuconta-003.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b4576ddc1d9bf0630052d48d69d817d2/44727/nuconta-003.png 450w,\n/static/b4576ddc1d9bf0630052d48d69d817d2/fea0e/nuconta-003.png 900w,\n/static/b4576ddc1d9bf0630052d48d69d817d2/79a4a/nuconta-003.png 1800w,\n/static/b4576ddc1d9bf0630052d48d69d817d2/a987b/nuconta-003.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.35232383808096%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 0009\"\n        title=\"nuconta 0009\"\n        src=\"/static/df0803e4b5c53f04c3dad6b9a6fc9a4b/79a4a/nuconta-0009.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df0803e4b5c53f04c3dad6b9a6fc9a4b/44727/nuconta-0009.png 450w,\n/static/df0803e4b5c53f04c3dad6b9a6fc9a4b/fea0e/nuconta-0009.png 900w,\n/static/df0803e4b5c53f04c3dad6b9a6fc9a4b/79a4a/nuconta-0009.png 1800w,\n/static/df0803e4b5c53f04c3dad6b9a6fc9a4b/59ec6/nuconta-0009.png 2668w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.014274981217135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 0019\"\n        title=\"nuconta 0019\"\n        src=\"/static/07c9208f26ad94a33b689d8b3ae88dad/79a4a/nuconta-0019.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/07c9208f26ad94a33b689d8b3ae88dad/44727/nuconta-0019.png 450w,\n/static/07c9208f26ad94a33b689d8b3ae88dad/fea0e/nuconta-0019.png 900w,\n/static/07c9208f26ad94a33b689d8b3ae88dad/79a4a/nuconta-0019.png 1800w,\n/static/07c9208f26ad94a33b689d8b3ae88dad/cd75e/nuconta-0019.png 2662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h2>Problem discovery</h2>\n<p>We were committed to challenging our most basic assumptions about how people understand and use banking services, so our initial conversations were purposefully broad and naive. We started with a simple list of questions, but we frequently adjusted along the way.</p>\n<p>We ran in-depth interviews with people from different ages and backgrounds in the office, but also on public places like malls and a public university. We sat down and very informally let people talk about their financial lives, how they felt about saving, investing, transferring, and spending their money. We also experimented with some visual aids such as card-sorting and very cheap prototypes, but honestly, our best feedback tools were our competitor’s websites and products. We learned an incredible amount just by having people experiment with things other companies have already built.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 009\"\n        title=\"nuconta 009\"\n        src=\"/static/16bc342b0c556e86bb9dbf6c3569ff75/8ff1e/nuconta-009.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/16bc342b0c556e86bb9dbf6c3569ff75/44727/nuconta-009.png 450w,\n/static/16bc342b0c556e86bb9dbf6c3569ff75/8ff1e/nuconta-009.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.55389221556886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta research\"\n        title=\"nuconta research\"\n        src=\"/static/0c90a8c7ecbc1a2d8ac17f46ab65415a/79a4a/nuconta-research.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0c90a8c7ecbc1a2d8ac17f46ab65415a/44727/nuconta-research.png 450w,\n/static/0c90a8c7ecbc1a2d8ac17f46ab65415a/fea0e/nuconta-research.png 900w,\n/static/0c90a8c7ecbc1a2d8ac17f46ab65415a/79a4a/nuconta-research.png 1800w,\n/static/0c90a8c7ecbc1a2d8ac17f46ab65415a/c7959/nuconta-research.png 2672w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<h2>Problem definition</h2>\n<p>By combining the data from these interviews with others conducted in our lab, and also talking to a lot of our employees about their finances, we were able to come up with eight personas that represent a gradient of behavior and demographic patterns.</p>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1554px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.5045045045045%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Our set of personas based on interviews and data\"\n        title=\"Our set of personas based on interviews and data\"\n        src=\"/static/9f3328f7cfb5a02d5fe0ca1b5e39ee30/fce90/nuconta-019.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9f3328f7cfb5a02d5fe0ca1b5e39ee30/44727/nuconta-019.png 450w,\n/static/9f3328f7cfb5a02d5fe0ca1b5e39ee30/fea0e/nuconta-019.png 900w,\n/static/9f3328f7cfb5a02d5fe0ca1b5e39ee30/fce90/nuconta-019.png 1554w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1554px) 100vw, 1554px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Our set of personas based on interviews and data</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<p>With well-defined personas, we now had a lens through which we could look at the problem. Our initial mission, which was very broad, could now be better expressed in sentences that the whole team could agree on:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>How might we design an evolution of the current and savings accounts, for people looking for a more accessible and easy-to-use bank?</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>We learned from this process that defining a problem is sometimes harder than sitting down to solve it. After dozens of long work days, heated meetings, lots of head-scratching, word-smithing, and sense-making about the material collected during research, the team was finally committed to a unified vision of the product that reflected our customer’s pains and needs instead of our own. We were now ready to deep dive into exploring solutions that would eventually become NuConta.</p>\n<h2>Generating solutions</h2>\n<p>The first thing we do at Nubank once we have a sound problem definition is what we call a co-design session, which helps us come up with more ideas, better questions, surface constraints and strong stakeholder opinions.</p>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1280px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 020\"\n        title=\"nuconta 020\"\n        src=\"/static/41a68c90f978221a082bfaea9cdc484e/0309e/nuconta-020.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41a68c90f978221a082bfaea9cdc484e/44727/nuconta-020.png 450w,\n/static/41a68c90f978221a082bfaea9cdc484e/fea0e/nuconta-020.png 900w,\n/static/41a68c90f978221a082bfaea9cdc484e/0309e/nuconta-020.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 021\"\n        title=\"nuconta 021\"\n        src=\"/static/be3878525d0099164cf4d033dc160d15/c35de/nuconta-021.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/be3878525d0099164cf4d033dc160d15/df2c7/nuconta-021.jpg 450w,\n/static/be3878525d0099164cf4d033dc160d15/2d017/nuconta-021.jpg 900w,\n/static/be3878525d0099164cf4d033dc160d15/c35de/nuconta-021.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.91666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 022\"\n        title=\"nuconta 022\"\n        src=\"/static/b29e9422735d4a5ef5fc88cfdf39c698/6ff5e/nuconta-022.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b29e9422735d4a5ef5fc88cfdf39c698/44727/nuconta-022.png 450w,\n/static/b29e9422735d4a5ef5fc88cfdf39c698/fea0e/nuconta-022.png 900w,\n/static/b29e9422735d4a5ef5fc88cfdf39c698/6ff5e/nuconta-022.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1280px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nuconta 023\"\n        title=\"nuconta 023\"\n        src=\"/static/3841f19bdef61c36993e20476b87208f/0309e/nuconta-023.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3841f19bdef61c36993e20476b87208f/44727/nuconta-023.png 450w,\n/static/3841f19bdef61c36993e20476b87208f/fea0e/nuconta-023.png 900w,\n/static/3841f19bdef61c36993e20476b87208f/0309e/nuconta-023.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<p>Based on the ideas generated by the team, we started the deepest dive I’ve ever taken on product design exploration. In many ways, both from a technical and a product perspective, NuConta does not fit squarely into a checking, savings or investment account “box”, so we found it a real challenge to align the interface with a user’s pre-existing mental models about money management. A new paradigm for how the money was going to be kept and used required a lot of hard thinking about accounting and how to best represent it on a screen. Given this potential complexity, we spent most of this time collaborating at the white-board without touching a digital design tool.</p>\n<p>Only after extensive discussion and brainstorming, we felt ready to start wireframes and pixel pushing: we tried dozens of versions of the UI of onboarding flows, empty states, investment simulators, charts (OMG so many charts), financial goals, investment streaks, etc. We allowed ourselves to go quite crazy in the beginning, bypassing many rules of our current design system, and then adjusted as we got closer to the final result.</p>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1280px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 259.53125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"So many explorations!\"\n        title=\"So many explorations!\"\n        src=\"/static/d077624f1e45d56baedf1e6301f3e98b/0309e/nuconta-024.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d077624f1e45d56baedf1e6301f3e98b/44727/nuconta-024.png 450w,\n/static/d077624f1e45d56baedf1e6301f3e98b/fea0e/nuconta-024.png 900w,\n/static/d077624f1e45d56baedf1e6301f3e98b/0309e/nuconta-024.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">So many explorations!</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<h3>Prototyping</h3>\n<p>We made every kind of prototype you could imagine when exploring solutions for NuConta. We made cheap paper prototypes to test copywriting and general information architecture. We made quick Keynote animations to show engineers the vision for a specific interaction. We built screens and flows on Principle to test signup flows and empty states. Some prototypes even had fake branding and visuals so we could go outside the building and show it around in stealth mode.</p>\n<p>Starting with simpler, lower fidelity prototypes allowed us to trim the rough edges of the product overall concept, until we eventually hit a level of complexity in the tests that required a more high fidelity, versatile prototype. So we decided to invest in a month-long project to create a full-blown Framer + Javascript prototype that passed variables around, reacted to the user’s financial data, and let them simulate deposits. This was of course not just the work of our design team but a coordinated effort with the technical team to support us not only in programming the prototype but also in user-testing it and iterating on the results.</p>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1280px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.265625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Paper prototypes\"\n        title=\"Paper prototypes\"\n        src=\"/static/9e891172fdc22c2a260ffc94da8a8682/0309e/nuconta-025.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9e891172fdc22c2a260ffc94da8a8682/44727/nuconta-025.png 450w,\n/static/9e891172fdc22c2a260ffc94da8a8682/fea0e/nuconta-025.png 900w,\n/static/9e891172fdc22c2a260ffc94da8a8682/0309e/nuconta-025.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Paper prototypes</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<!-- ![](../../images/nubank/nuconta-027.gif) -->\n<h2>Delivering the MVP</h2>\n<h4>Designing for transparency, with transparency</h4>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"To increase transparency and collaboration, we fully transitioned to Figma during Nuconta&#39;s development\"\n        title=\"To increase transparency and collaboration, we fully transitioned to Figma during Nuconta&#39;s development\"\n        src=\"/static/feb495fce57c02521d94e0018100802b/79a4a/nuconta-028.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/feb495fce57c02521d94e0018100802b/44727/nuconta-028.png 450w,\n/static/feb495fce57c02521d94e0018100802b/fea0e/nuconta-028.png 900w,\n/static/feb495fce57c02521d94e0018100802b/79a4a/nuconta-028.png 1800w,\n/static/feb495fce57c02521d94e0018100802b/d40c8/nuconta-028.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">To increase transparency and collaboration, we fully transitioned to Figma during Nuconta&#39;s development</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<p>One key component of the speed and quality of our workflow in this project was to use Figma in the early stages of the UI design process, because of the high level of collaboration and transparency it allows. Just like our live streamed user tests, Figma makes it frictionless for stakeholders to watch, participate, and gain empathy for the design process in real time.</p>\n<h4>Mapping the whole experience</h4>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1658px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.13630880579011%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Mapping the launch experience across Website, App, Social Media, Support, and Emails \"\n        title=\"Mapping the launch experience across Website, App, Social Media, Support, and Emails \"\n        src=\"/static/af2386d0f90bf9a46d05184a89f2e8ac/241f5/nuconta-029.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af2386d0f90bf9a46d05184a89f2e8ac/44727/nuconta-029.png 450w,\n/static/af2386d0f90bf9a46d05184a89f2e8ac/fea0e/nuconta-029.png 900w,\n/static/af2386d0f90bf9a46d05184a89f2e8ac/241f5/nuconta-029.png 1658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1658px) 100vw, 1658px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Mapping the launch experience across Website, App, Social Media, Support, and Emails </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<p>Producing a well-crafted individual screen is satisfying, but we can never forget that every touchpoint is part of a broader ecosystem. Below is an example of how we kept track of every App screen, push notification, email, website page, and social media posts that first-time users would encounter.</p>\n<h2>Nuconta becomes the most downloaded banking app in the world.</h2>\n<p>In an October report, Quartz noted that Nubank’s app has been downloaded 18 million times in the past year, more than Revolut, Monzo, and N26 combined. Nubank’s monthly active users have risen 200% during that period, second only to Monzo.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"September 04, 2017","path":"/blog/nubank/nuconta","title":"Nubank Savings","topics":["Product Design","Research"],"subtitle":"Designing the largest digital banking app in the world","problem":"Brazilians are stuck with terrible banking account options.","solution":"A free, integrated, hybrid checking and savings account.","impact":"10+ Million customers in the 1st year of launch.","color":"#BB6BD9","where":"São Paulo","learn_more":"http://nubank.com.br/nuconta","team":["Rachel Jordan","Erick Mazer","Vitor Gurgel"],"myrole":"Co-led the 0-to-1 yearlong design process.","link":null,"cover_image":{"publicURL":"/static/nuconta-hero-4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675.png","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/54c56/nuconta-hero.png","srcSet":"/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/16256/nuconta-hero.png 175w,\n/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/73897/nuconta-hero.png 350w,\n/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/54c56/nuconta-hero.png 700w,\n/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/c0798/nuconta-hero.png 1050w,\n/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/cd9a9/nuconta-hero.png 1400w,\n/static/4cd84fe05593feb33f64e80e6f057675/155f2/nuconta-hero.png 6400w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/blog/nubank/design-team","title":"Design Team Principles","subtitle":"Defining why and how we work","cover_image":{"publicURL":"/static/nubank-team-logo-f697cbb16aa697a783d4d0097acb51cd.png"}}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/blog/others/goldenart","title":"GoldenArt","subtitle":"My family's company website, my code sandbox.","cover_image":{"publicURL":"/static/golden-art-hero-2-181483404ea55acba4d3d44ac4836e09.png"}}}}}}